name: Gather Community Plant #001 - Lord Stingray
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from HicEtNunc artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Lord Stingray is an animator who has worked with artists including Juice WRLD, Trippie Redd, Bladee, CARTIER'GOD, Lil Darkie, and more. His unique, mysterious, and nostalgic style reminds one of a classic Playstation video game. Young and filled with talent it will be exciting where Lord Stingray's career will take him in the animation game.

Buying this plant directly funds the GatherArt Foundation & the artist who planted this CleanNFT.
